# Cloudflare / Netlify rewrites.
# Serve the "app not installed" fallback for any shared-recipe link.
# When Oqra IS installed, iOS opens the app before the browser ever loads this.
# The target lives OUTSIDE /p/ so the rule can't match its own destination
# (a destination under /p/ would re-trigger /p/* — an infinite loop Cloudflare rejects).
# Target is the extensionless path (Cloudflare strips .html and serves /shared),
# so this is a clean 200 rewrite with no redirect hop.
/p/*  /shared  200
